[TestOCIArchiveValidate/digest_missing_algorithm_prefix - 1]
OCIArchive.Digest: Invalid value: e3b0c44298fc1c149afbf4c8996fb92427ae41e4649b934ca495991b7852b855: [digest must be of the form sha256:<64 lowercase hex chars>]
---

